  "texts": [
    "This study also faced some limitations that must be acknowledged.",
    "First, to make our trained ensemble ML model efficient and transferable, the same (or similar) list of variables must be collected in the new location.",
    "Unfortunately, extracting long time-series data (i.e., 20 years of DIR for Brazil) is not possible in other countries.",
    "This is why we demonstrated how we transferred our ensemble model to Peru, which had half of this temporal length and administrative units with available data.",
    "Second, we did not work with all departments in Peru; therefore, it was not feasible to compute the spatial correlation through the CNN-based pre-processing step."
  ],
